reviewText: Veggietales is a wonderful show and this DVD is just as good. The songs are hilarious and will keep the kids entertained for quite some time.

reviewText: These silly songs have been a great source of entertainment for many kiddos that have come to my home. Good buy.

reviewText: Funny stuff.  My 95 yo Mom loves watching these when there is nothing else on TV, which there very rarely is these days.
Title: Veggie Tales: Very Silly Songs

reviewText: THE ORIGINAL "SILLY SONGS" WAS JUST THAT, SILLY SONGS.  LOVE THE SONGS ABOUT PIRATES, LIPS AND HAIRBRUSHES, BUT, THIS REMASTER SEEMS TO THROW IN SOME OF THE BIBLICAL SONGS.  I AM NOT A FAN OF THE VEGGIE TALES GOD SONGS, AND THOUGHT THIS ONE WAS JUST THE "SILLY SONGS" CD.  JUDITH
Title: Veggie Tales: Very Silly Songs

reviewText: I purchased "Very Silly Songs" for my grandson. They are fun songs, upbeat, and have a message about God in them. I am pleased, and he liked to dance to the music.
Title: Veggie Tales: Very Silly Songs

reviewText: you cannot go wrong buying Veggie Tales for  your children between ages 1-4.  My 2 year old grand daughter loves each and every Veggie Tale book and movie so I highly recommend.
Title: Veggie Tales: Very Silly Songs

reviewText: Our two year old LOVES music and dancing to silly songs. This compliments all of his loves. He watched the whole disc just engrossed, laughing and occasionally dancing but not too much to distract from the silly veggie songs. Definitely recommend for any child / parent age 0+. I believe you can take it in the car or portable CD player too, we will try that next.Follow @nissawise
Title: Veggie Tales: Very Silly Songs

reviewText: Veggie Tales is my favorite! I recommend all their products very highly. Not only is everything funny but there is always a positive message. This is a CD of songs from the DVDs. The best song is "I Love My Lips"-it's hysterical! From the youngest ones to your bigger kids, they will all be fans. Buy this, you'll be glad you did!
summary: How Could You Not Love This?
